    <h2 class="text-primary" id="heading">Heading</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>
      To create a heading, you can add one to six <mark>#</mark> symbols before your heading text. The number of <mark>#</mark> you use will determine the size of the heading.
    </p>
    <h3>Example</h3>
    <hr>
    <pre>
      # Heading 1 <br>
      ## Heading 2 <br>
      ### Heading 3 <br>
      #### Heading 4 <br>
      ##### Heading 5 <br>
      ###### Heading 6 <br>
    </pre>
    <h3>Preview</h3>
    <hr>
    <p>
      <h1>Heading 1</h1>
      <h2>Heading 2</h2>
      <h3>Heading 3</h3>
      <h4>Heading 4</h4>
      <h5>Heading 5</h5>
